'''黎义恩'''（英文名：{{lang|en|'''Ted Lipman'''}}，{{bd|1953年||||catIdx=Lipman}}），[[加拿大|加拿大]]外交官，现任加拿大驻[[朝鲜|朝鲜]]和[[韩国|韩国]]大使。<ref name="ST">{{cite news|url=http://theseoultimes.com/ST/?url=/ST/db/read.php?idx=5863|title=Canada Opens New Embassy in Jeong-dong|work=[[首爾時報|首爾時報]]|accessdate=8 February 2010|archive-date=2018-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181028073807/http://theseoultimes.com/ST/?url=%2FST%2Fdb%2Fread.php%3Fidx%3D5863|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thestar.com/News/World/article/297617|title=Ottawa urged to aid N. Korea captive|last=Ferenc|first=Leslie|date=28 January 2008|work=[[多倫多星報|多倫多星報]]|accessdate=8 February 2010|archive-date=2010-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100211113612/http://www.thestar.com/News/World/article/297617|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.legionmagazine.com/en/index.php/2008/11/korea-tension-and-remembrance/|title=Korea: Tension And Remembrance|last=MacGregor|first=Tom|date=15 November 2008|work=Legion Magazine|accessdate=8 February 2010|archive-date=2010-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100211135847/http://www.legionmagazine.com/en/index.php/2008/11/korea-tension-and-remembrance/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他出生于[[巴西|巴西]]，在[[里约热内卢|里约热内卢]]、[[英国|英国]]和[[温哥华|温哥华]]长大。黎义恩曾在[[不列颠哥伦比亚大学|不列颠哥伦比亚大学]]学习亚洲研究，后在[[北京大学|北京大学]]学习中国历史。20世纪80、90年代，他在[[中国|中国]]任职，担任过加拿大驻[[上海|上海]]总领事、加拿大驻華大使馆[[公使|公使]]。<ref name="ST" />2001年至2004年间，他前往[[台湾|台湾]]，任[[加拿大驻台北贸易办事处|加拿大驻台北贸易办事处]]代表。<ref name="ST"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2003/11/01/2003074170|title=Legislators form bipartisan Canadian group|date=1 November 2003|work=[[Taipei_Times|Taipei Times]]|accessdate=8 February 2010|archive-date=2010-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100211220834/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2003/11/01/2003074170|dead-url=no}}</ref>

黎义恩的妻子是著名中国女歌手[[朱哲琴|朱哲琴]]。<ref name="hq">{{cite web|url=http://www.gcpnews.com/articles/2007-05-08/C1040_10224.html|title=中国新音乐代表人物朱哲琴将到温哥华开唱|publisher=环球华网|accessdate=2010-02-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100105000655/http://www.gcpnews.com/articles/2007-05-08/C1040_10224.html|archivedate=2010-01-05}}</ref>

